  "text": "In the last session Ra stated that \"the path back from sixth-density negative time/space revolves, firstly, about the higher self's reluctance to enter negative time/space. \" Could you explain the higher self's position with respect to positive and negative time/space and why it is so reluctant to enter negative time/space that it is necessary for the mind/body/spirit complex to incarnate in negative space/time to find its path back? I am Ra. In brief, you have answered your own query. Please question further for more precise information.",
